# Rust / Cargo build artifacts
/target/
**/target/
# NOTE: Cargo.lock IS committed on purpose. The pinned toolchain is Rust 1.81.0,
# and several transitive crates have since published versions requiring
# edition2024 / rustc >= 1.82 (indexmap, getrandom, base64ct, blake2b_simd,
# zeroize_derive, backtrace, cxx, ed25519-zebra, tempfile, proc-macro-crate…).
# The lockfile pins them to their last 1.81-compatible releases; a fresh
# `cargo update` of those would re-break the build. Do not ignore Cargo.lock.

# Substrate / node local data
.chain-data/
*.db/
rocksdb/

# Editor / OS
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# WASM build intermediates
**/*.wasm.bin
